# 🔐 Telegram String Session Generator Bot

A secure and user-friendly Telegram bot that allows users to generate their own **Pyrogram String Session** safely.

## ✨ Features

- 🔑 Generate Pyrogram String Sessions
- 📱 Phone Number Verification
- 🔢 OTP Verification
- 🛡️ Two-Step Verification (2FA) Support
- ⚡ Fast & Secure Session Generation
- ❌ Cancel Current Process
- ⏱️ Session Timeout Handling
- 🚫 Rate Limiting
- 📊 Admin Statistics
- 📢 Broadcast Support
- 📝 Clean & Structured Logging
- ☁️ Render Ready
- 🐍 Python 3.11+
- 🚀 GitHub Ready

