## 🚀 Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/your-repository.git
cd your-repository
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Configure Environment

Rename:

```
.env.example
```

to

```
.env
```

and configure your values.

---

## ▶️ Run

```bash
python bot.py
```

