## 🔒 Security

- No permanent storage of generated String Sessions.
- Sensitive user information is never logged.
- Secure OTP & 2FA handling.
- Automatic cleanup of temporary data.

---

## 📜 Disclaimer

This project is intended **only for users to generate a session for their own Telegram account**. Users are responsible for keeping their generated String Session private. Misuse of this project is the sole responsibility of the user.

